### Architecture of the Project

![architecture](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35001929/77555241-0bba5500-6f27-11ea-9c9d-f47e67f2b2ab.png)


### Tech stack

#### Frontend
* React
* Redux

#### Backend
* Node js

#### Database
* MongoDB


## Installation

* Clone the Repository
* Open two terminals in the root folder
* One terminal for server, run the following command 
```
npm install
npm run start
```
* Second terminal for client, run the following command
```
cd client
npm install
npm run start
```


## Dependencies

* node-cron
* nodemailer
* redux
